Project Euler #1
https://projecteuler.net/problem=1

If we list all the natural numbers below 10 that are multiples of 3 or 5, we get 3, 5, 6 and 9. The sum of these multiples is 23.

Find the sum of all the multiples of 3 or 5 below 1000.
blockcomment

variable limit is one zero zero zero

variable counter is one
variable total is zero

while counter lessthan limit do
    if counter modulo three equals zero or counter modulo five equals zero
        variable total is total plus counter
    fi
    variable counter is counter plus one
end

print total